issue_body:
**Input code**

```ts
declare namespace __event {
    export class EventInit {
        constructor({
            bubbles,
            cancelable,
            composed
        }?: {
            bubbles?: boolean | undefined;
            cancelable?: boolean | undefined;
            composed?: boolean | undefined;
        });
    }
}
```

**Expected behavior**

No error, as this is not an implementation signature since this is an ambient context.

**Actual behavior**

Has diagnostic: `A binding pattern parameter cannot be optional in an implementation signature.`

**Version**
The version of @swc/core: latest
